com.interpss.core.aclf.adj
Interface RemoteQBus

All Superinterfaces:
AclfControlBus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PVBusLimit
All Known Implementing Classes:
RemoteQBusImpl
public interface RemoteQBus
extends PVBusLimit

A representation of the model object 'Remote QBus'. Remote Q voltage control bus class. Use the bus Q (of this bus) to control the voltage of a remote bus or reactive power through a remote branch. The remote bus could be this bus itself, can not be a GenPV or Swing bus. RemoteQBus id is the same as the busId of this bus.

The following features are supported:

  • Control Type
  • Flow From2 To
  • Mvar On From Side
  • DQ dv
  • Acc Factor
  • Remote Bus
  • Remote Branch
